channel.title: Project Extracted - Alpha
channel.description:
Hello and welcome to Project Extracted!
Website - [url=http://projectextracted.com/index.php]http://projectextracted.com/index.php[/url]
Staff List:
Owner - Jason Co-Owner - Garrett Developer - Josh
Here we strive to listen to what the players want and are willing to give it to them. We also provide many of other things, including, but not limited to:
A fun, friendly atmosphere where players can come to compete, have fun, and simply chat it up with each other. A unique RSPS experience, with aspects you won't see anywhere else. Lots of things to do, where skilling and economy are the goal. We feature real bounty hunter styled PvP. We also have a unique minigame in the process, that you can earn rewards from. Tired of being low on cash? Try gambling! We feature a ton more of stuff, so why not come check us out to see what we have!
